title: Jessica Lange Throws Shade at Lady Gaga's Casting for American Horror Story: Hotel
author: AHS Leaks
comment: I really hate it when people pit two queens against each other.
so many things going on at once, Jessica's like, "umm dafuq" Sarah is like "Jessica we know what u wanna say but dont say it coz u drunk" and Evan is just like "lul"
I gotta admit, this was masterful shade.

Honestly I don't think she was showing any disrespect/shade. I think she was just confused by the question like many others have said. At this point I believe she was already saying she was leaving ahs before lady gaga was casted.
I don't deny it can be a shade but also.. she always answers like that
